               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾāmmǝra Māryām: I-1) Maṣḥafa śǝrʿāt, The introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fols.
                     5ra-6va)&#xD; I-2) ʾƎsaggǝd laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki “I worship Thee…” (fols.


                     6va-7ra)&#xD; I-3) Taʾammǝra Māryām “Miracles of Mary”: 93 miracles (fols.
                     2ra-4vb, 7ra-77ra)&#xD; II) Taʾammǝra Mikāʾel "Miracles of Michael": 1 miracle


                     (fols. 77rb-77vb)&#xD; &#xD; Colophon.</summary>
